'''etta''' is a [[Quenya]] conjunction meaning "therefore".<ref>{{VT|49a}}, p. 12</ref>
==Etymology==
Perhaps from ''[[et]]'' and ''[[ta]]''. In this case, the possible literal meaning is *"out of which".
